<br>
I would seriously question a claim about an ac penalty from behind.  But, the fact that the mob isn't using any of it's defensive skills from behind is -huge-. Log melee from the front, and watch the incidence of parry and riposte and dodges.  They happen quite often, and seriously take down your pets DPS. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:perpetua;font-size:x-small;">Turzem Setanta -- <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=421973">Arch Mage</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.insidiousblood.net">Insidious Blood</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rhasinfirestorm@themagicianstower>Rhasin Firestorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1208<br> <font color=#333333>(12/2/02 8:39:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8003.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Steel Warrior post .. Comments?</span><hr size=1> Add to this matter the fact that, often, pathing just simply does not permit easy positioning of a pet in confined spaces to place it at the mob's back.<br>
